about.summary: Package for hierarchical clustering of objects characterized by nominal variables.

name: r-nomclust
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.1.4" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-nomclust
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/nomclust_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/nomclust/nomclust_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5580cd281886dc53b0f23c83b6102e97e17624242f572ecc6f6bfd40369bf50b

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic

  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-cluster
    - r-plyr
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-cluster
    - r-plyr

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('nomclust')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('nomclust')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=nomclust
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Package for hierarchical clustering of objects characterized by nominal variables.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - uday1889
